Author: glangley
Title: Decision to store geocodes
Content:
I am working on a website and am planning on implementing a google map on each page and would need to make between 10-50 geocode requests on each page. Is it smart to have a whole new table just for storing these geocode address or is it easier to just hit google every page refresh?

Thanks in advance.
